19
00:00:17,564 --> 00:00:21,109
<i>Corruption, discovered at
the core of the Banking Clan.</i>

20
00:00:21,568 --> 00:00:24,279
<i>Reunited, Rush Clovis
and Senator Amidala</i>

21
00:00:24,362 --> 00:00:27,324
<i>discover the full extent
of the deception.</i>

22
00:00:27,407 --> 00:00:29,784
<i>Anakin Skywalker is sent to the rescue.</i>

23
00:00:30,660 --> 00:00:34,539
<i>He refuses to trust Clovis and
asks Padmé not to work with him.</i>

24
00:00:34,831 --> 00:00:38,793
<i>Determined to save the banks,
she refuses her husband's request,</i>

25
00:00:38,877 --> 00:00:41,796
<i>throwing their relationship into turmoil.</i>

26
00:00:42,464 --> 00:00:45,383
<i>Voted for by both
the Separatists and the Republic,</i>

27
00:00:45,467 --> 00:00:49,387
<i>Rush Clovis is elected new leader
of the Galactic Banking Clan.</i>

28
00:00:49,971 --> 00:00:52,974
<i>Now, all attention is focused on Scipio,</i>

29
00:00:53,058 --> 00:00:56,144
<i>as the important
transfer of power begins.</i>

30
00:01:20,168 --> 00:01:22,921
Welcome back to Scipio, Rush Clovis.

31
00:01:24,047 --> 00:01:26,716
Our Separatist government has
great hopes for you.

32
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:28,051
Thank you, Senator.

33
00:01:29,678 --> 00:01:31,638
Only you and Senator Amidala
will be allowed

34
00:01:31,721 --> 00:01:33,807
to monitor the exchange proceedings.

35
00:01:34,349 --> 00:01:38,228
No forces on either side
will be allowed into the neutral zone.

36
00:01:38,311 --> 00:01:41,481
<i>Senator Amidala, we'll be right here
if you should need us.</i>

37
00:01:41,564 --> 00:01:43,358
Thank you, Commander.

38
00:02:06,381 --> 00:02:11,469
<i>It is with great disappointment
that I implement the following verdict.</i>

39
00:02:12,804 --> 00:02:15,140
<i>By decree of the Muun people,</i>

40
00:02:15,223 --> 00:02:18,310
<i>the five representatives
standing before me</i>

41
00:02:18,393 --> 00:02:20,937
<i>are found guilty of embezzlement.</i>

42
00:02:21,396 --> 00:02:23,940
<i>They shall be imprisoned forthwith,</i>

43
00:02:24,024 --> 00:02:29,112
<i>and control of the banks shall
transfer immediately to Rush Clovis,</i>

44
00:02:29,195 --> 00:02:32,574
<i>under the guidance of
the Muun government.</i>

45
00:02:40,915 --> 00:02:42,959
<i>We are grateful to you, Clovis,</i>

46
00:02:43,043 --> 00:02:46,171
<i>for everything you have
done for the Muun people.</i>

47
00:02:46,629 --> 00:02:50,508
<i>To have lost the banks
would have been a historic disaster.</i>

48
00:02:51,092 --> 00:02:54,429
I would like you to know I have
no interest in controlling the banks.

49
00:02:54,846 --> 00:02:57,515
<i>I'm simply here to reestablish order.</i>

50
00:03:02,103 --> 00:03:05,065
Do you think our friend
is up to the task?

51
00:03:05,899 --> 00:03:07,776
There are few men
I have met in my career

52
00:03:07,859 --> 00:03:10,278
who are more dedicated to a cause
than Clovis.

53
00:03:10,612 --> 00:03:14,908
Once he decides what he is fighting for,
little will stop him from achieving it.

54
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:18,703
Let us hope you are right,
for all our sakes.

55
00:03:39,641 --> 00:03:43,436
<i>Clovis, how are you liking
your new office?</i>

56
00:03:43,812 --> 00:03:47,649
<i>I must say, you look very comfortable
behind that desk.</i>

57
00:03:47,732 --> 00:03:50,652
Count Dooku,
what do I owe the pleasure?

58
00:03:51,069 --> 00:03:53,113
<i>Come, come, my boy.</i>

59
00:03:53,196 --> 00:03:55,573
<i>You don't think
I'd let such an important day pass</i>

60
00:03:55,657 --> 00:03:58,201
<i>without wishing you the best of luck?</i>

61
00:03:58,660 --> 00:04:01,496
Thank you.
But luck has nothing to do with it.

62
00:04:01,579 --> 00:04:03,915
The transfer has occurred
without a hitch.

63
00:04:03,998 --> 00:04:05,708
<i>Well, of course it has.</i>

64
00:04:05,792 --> 00:04:09,087
<i>The Separatists are
fully behind your appointment.</i>

65
00:04:09,170 --> 00:04:12,549
<i>After all, aren't we
the ones who put you there?</i>

66
00:04:14,342 --> 00:04:16,136
For your support, I am grateful.

67
00:04:16,219 --> 00:04:19,347
But I now must lead
without allegiance towards either side.

68
00:04:22,183 --> 00:04:24,102
<i>Is that so?</i>

69
00:04:24,185 --> 00:04:27,605
<i>Quite the idealist you have become
in so short a time.</i>

70
00:04:28,106 --> 00:04:30,066
What do you want, Dooku?

71
00:04:30,191 --> 00:04:32,277
<i>To collect on my investment.</i>

72
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:34,279
<i>How do you think
the Republic would like to know</i>

73
00:04:34,362 --> 00:04:36,948
<i>that it was I who supplied Rush Clovis</i>

74
00:04:37,031 --> 00:04:40,660
<i>with all the information he needed
to topple the leaders of the bank?</i>

75
00:04:40,743 --> 00:04:42,579
I will tell them myself.

76
00:04:42,662 --> 00:04:44,205
<i>But you can't.</i>

77
00:04:44,664 --> 00:04:48,334
<i>I put you in power, you belong to me.</i>

78
00:04:49,002 --> 00:04:52,380
<i>And if you want to stay in control,
you will do as I say.</i>

79
00:04:52,797 --> 00:04:55,216
The banks will remain unbiased.

80
00:04:55,842 --> 00:05:00,805
<i>Then I'm afraid the Separatists will be
unable to pay the interest on our loans.</i>

81
00:05:01,055 --> 00:05:03,016
But the banks will collapse and the...

82
00:05:03,099 --> 00:05:06,436
<i>Not if you raise interest rates
on the Republic.</i>

83
00:05:06,561 --> 00:05:07,562
What?

84
00:05:07,812 --> 00:05:09,272
You know I can't do that.

85
00:05:09,564 --> 00:05:12,150
<i>But you can, and you will.</i>

86
00:05:12,442 --> 00:05:16,946
<i>Or everything that you've fought
so hard for will be destroyed.</i>

87
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:33,505
By the new order of the Traxus Division,

88
00:05:33,671 --> 00:05:35,882
<i>and in an attempt
to stabilize the banks,</i>

89
00:05:36,257 --> 00:05:39,177
<i>it is essential that interest rates on
loans to the Republic</i>

90
00:05:39,260 --> 00:05:40,845
<i>be raised immediately.</i>

91
00:05:41,763 --> 00:05:42,805
What?

92
00:05:43,014 --> 00:05:44,224
But you can't do that!

93
00:05:44,599 --> 00:05:45,600
Clovis!

94
00:05:46,476 --> 00:05:47,560
Clovis?

95
00:05:47,936 --> 00:05:49,687
What are you doing?

96
00:06:03,785 --> 00:06:05,328
<i>This is an outrage!</i>

97
00:06:05,453 --> 00:06:07,580
<i>We warned you this would happen!</i>

98
00:06:07,664 --> 00:06:09,874
<i>And what of the Separatists?</i>

99
00:06:10,333 --> 00:06:14,128
<i>From the little information Senator
Amidala has been able to establish,</i>

100
00:06:14,212 --> 00:06:17,423
<i>there will be no raise
on their current loan.</i>

101
00:06:18,091 --> 00:06:21,636
<i>I knew from the beginning
that Clovis would do this.</i>

102
00:06:22,095 --> 00:06:24,472
<i>We knew that Clovis would do this.</i>

103
00:06:29,435 --> 00:06:32,188
Correct you might have been
about Clovis.

104
00:06:32,772 --> 00:06:36,067
It's incredibly foolish for him
to make a move like this so early.

105
00:06:36,317 --> 00:06:39,028
He will turn the whole Republic
against him.

106
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:44,117
Not clear to us are his objectives.
Want this, he might.

107
00:06:44,909 --> 00:06:48,037
Something's wrong.
This doesn't make sense.

108
00:06:48,454 --> 00:06:51,708
<i>I would like to call for restraint</i>

109
00:06:51,791 --> 00:06:54,752
<i>and allow us time
to analyze the situation.</i>

110
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:14,397
You may begin your attack.

111
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:19,444
It is time to make Rush Clovis
look like a powerful Separatist.

112
00:07:19,527 --> 00:07:21,279
Right away, sir.

113
00:07:28,077 --> 00:07:29,621
It looks like an invasion fleet, sir.

114
00:07:29,871 --> 00:07:31,623
We're caught out here in the open.

115
00:07:36,336 --> 00:07:39,672
Get the men off this landing pad
and beyond the city gates.

116
00:07:50,850 --> 00:07:53,353
<i>Senator Amidala, come in, please.</i>

117
00:07:53,436 --> 00:07:54,812
What is it, Commander Thorn?

118
00:07:54,896 --> 00:07:57,148
<i>We're under attack
by the Separatist garrison.</i>

119
00:07:57,482 --> 00:07:58,900
<i>Looks to be a full invasion.</i>

120
00:07:59,108 --> 00:08:00,401
Invasion?

121
00:08:00,485 --> 00:08:01,778
<i>We can't get to you.</i>

122
00:08:01,861 --> 00:08:04,739
<i>I suggest you get to a ship
as soon as you can.</i>

123
00:08:28,221 --> 00:08:30,139
Let's move! Hurry!

124
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:00,753
For the Republic!

125
00:09:34,287 --> 00:09:36,914
<i>Our garrison has been
attacked by the Separatists.</i>

126
00:09:36,998 --> 00:09:39,417
<i>And it appears
they are staging an invasion of Scipio.</i>

127
00:09:39,500 --> 00:09:40,877
An invasion?

128
00:09:41,252 --> 00:09:42,837
What do they hope to achieve?

129
00:09:43,337 --> 00:09:46,966
With this news, the Senate will
vote immediately to attack Scipio.

130
00:09:47,300 --> 00:09:49,927
<i>It appears war has
already come to Scipio.</i>

131
00:09:50,178 --> 00:09:52,180
I want you off that planet immediately.

132
00:09:52,513 --> 00:09:53,681
<i>I can't.</i>

133
00:09:54,140 --> 00:09:55,933
Surely you can get to a ship.

134
00:09:56,392 --> 00:09:59,228
<i>General Skywalker,
I'm afraid I'm trapped.</i>

135
00:10:03,024 --> 00:10:04,025
<i>Let me go!</i>

136
00:10:05,276 --> 00:10:07,445
Invoke an emergency meeting
of the Senate.

137
00:10:07,528 --> 00:10:09,363
There is no time to lose.

138
00:10:11,574 --> 00:10:15,703
I feel it is only right that you should
handle this matter, my boy.

139
00:10:15,787 --> 00:10:18,206
A lot will be entrusted to you.

140
00:10:26,172 --> 00:10:27,256
Don't touch me.

141
00:10:29,550 --> 00:10:30,676
What have you done to her?

142
00:10:32,094 --> 00:10:34,597
Clovis, what is going on?

143
00:10:34,680 --> 00:10:36,641
I didn't want this, Padmé.

144
00:10:36,724 --> 00:10:40,478
Why don't you tell her
what you did want and how you got it.

145
00:10:41,687 --> 00:10:43,022
Dooku?

146
00:10:46,442 --> 00:10:48,486
Padmé, this is not what it seems.

147
00:10:48,569 --> 00:10:50,947
Hasn't she joined our cause?

148
00:10:51,030 --> 00:10:55,159
Clovis here told me how instrumental
you were in getting him to power.

149
00:10:55,243 --> 00:10:56,494
If I had known...

150
00:10:56,577 --> 00:10:59,205
Either you're with us,
or you're against us.

151
00:10:59,288 --> 00:11:00,581
Arrest her.

152
00:11:00,665 --> 00:11:02,250
We can't do this, Dooku.

153
00:11:02,583 --> 00:11:04,794
The Separatist Senate
will never approve.

154
00:11:06,003 --> 00:11:07,088
Hey.

155
00:11:11,801 --> 00:11:14,178
No, no!

156
00:11:16,264 --> 00:11:17,390
No!

157
00:11:19,475 --> 00:11:22,353
Are you insane?
This was not part of the deal.

158
00:11:22,436 --> 00:11:24,021
What deal?

159
00:11:24,105 --> 00:11:25,898
What have you done here, Clovis?

160
00:11:25,982 --> 00:11:27,525
He's given us the banks.

161
00:11:28,067 --> 00:11:32,113
Gone are our debts,
and gone is any credit for the Republic.

162
00:11:33,489 --> 00:11:36,409
All of your idealism was just a front.

163
00:11:36,951 --> 00:11:38,786
There was nothing I could do.

164
00:11:39,328 --> 00:11:42,373
Everyone has their price, my dear.

165
00:11:49,755 --> 00:11:53,175
<i>It is with grave news I come before you.</i>

166
00:11:53,885 --> 00:11:57,054
<i>Count Dooku and
his Separatist betrayers</i>

167
00:11:57,138 --> 00:11:59,140
<i>have manipulated us, my friends.</i>

168
00:11:59,765 --> 00:12:02,018
<i>The war must go to Scipio.</i>

169
00:12:02,101 --> 00:12:04,729
<i>Clovis has been their puppet of deceit,</i>

170
00:12:04,812 --> 00:12:08,941
<i>as the Separatists are
currently invading Scipio.</i>

171
00:12:09,025 --> 00:12:11,777
<i>We must stop them
and secure the planet.</i>

172
00:12:11,861 --> 00:12:16,866
<i>We have handed the entire
economic system over to Count Dooku.</i>

173
00:12:16,949 --> 00:12:19,577
<i>We are doomed! Invade!</i>

174
00:12:23,164 --> 00:12:25,166
<i>As Supreme Chancellor,</i>

175
00:12:25,249 --> 00:12:28,628
<i>I must abide
by the consensus of the Senate.</i>

176
00:12:28,711 --> 00:12:31,923
<i>We shall commence
a mercy mission to Scipio</i>

177
00:12:32,006 --> 00:12:35,217
<i>to be led by General Anakin Skywalker.</i>

178
00:12:36,010 --> 00:12:42,475
<i>The banks will be secured at all costs.
And the Republic will not crumble.</i>

179
00:12:44,393 --> 00:12:47,021
<i>We'll obtain victory!</i>

180
00:12:47,730 --> 00:12:50,608
<i>Yeah, war on Scipio.</i>

181
00:12:53,194 --> 00:12:57,698
Great emotions you will find on Scipio,
will you not?

182
00:12:59,575 --> 00:13:03,663
I am worried for Senator Amidala.
I'm afraid we may be too late.

183
00:13:03,913 --> 00:13:09,543
Correct you were about Clovis.
But let go of your selfishness you must

184
00:13:09,961 --> 00:13:12,004
if you are to see clearly.

185
00:13:12,546 --> 00:13:15,216
Not all is as it seems.

186
00:13:16,342 --> 00:13:18,177
I understand, Master.

187
00:13:45,579 --> 00:13:50,835
<i>Lord Tyranus, the Republic fleet
will be arriving shortly.</i>

188
00:13:51,210 --> 00:13:52,837
Very good, my Lord.

189
00:13:52,920 --> 00:13:55,631
Clovis has blindly played his part,

190
00:13:55,715 --> 00:13:59,635
it now appears he coordinated
the entire Separatist takeover.

191
00:14:00,886 --> 00:14:06,225
<i>And because of this treachery,
the banks will be firmly placed</i>

192
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:10,896
<i>under the control of
the Supreme Chancellor.</i>

193
00:14:24,285 --> 00:14:26,203
Why are you doing this?

194
00:14:26,287 --> 00:14:28,414
You wouldn't understand.

195
00:14:28,873 --> 00:14:33,419
I had to strike a deal with Dooku.
But don't worry, I am the one in control.

196
00:14:33,502 --> 00:14:36,213
As soon as things have settled down,
I can get rid of him.

197
00:14:36,297 --> 00:14:37,965
And I'll control it all again.

198
00:14:38,049 --> 00:14:39,383
Listen to yourself.

199
00:14:39,467 --> 00:14:42,887
The Republic is sending its armada
to take back the banks.

200
00:14:42,970 --> 00:14:46,599
You've brought war
right where there cannot be war.

201
00:14:46,682 --> 00:14:50,019
Your actions have destroyed the banks
once and for all.

202
00:15:00,529 --> 00:15:03,491
Rex, have you gotten a fix
on Senator Amidala's position?

203
00:15:03,991 --> 00:15:06,243
We'll have a better lock
once we get near the city.

204
00:15:06,327 --> 00:15:08,829
But initial scans suggest
she's still alive, sir.

205
00:15:09,371 --> 00:15:10,414
Good.

206
00:15:10,498 --> 00:15:13,000
Hawk, we're gonna need air support
once we're on the ground.

207
00:15:13,209 --> 00:15:16,337
You'll have it, General.
Me and the boys are ready to fly.

208
00:15:52,373 --> 00:15:55,960
My Lord, we have
fully engaged Republic forces.

209
00:15:56,043 --> 00:15:58,462
But we are suffering heavy losses.

210
00:15:58,546 --> 00:16:00,798
We have accomplished
what we came here for.

211
00:16:00,881 --> 00:16:02,716
It is time to withdraw.

212
00:16:02,800 --> 00:16:07,721
But, sir, our forces are
still engaged in battle on the planet.

213
00:16:08,264 --> 00:16:09,515
Leave them.

214
00:16:09,849 --> 00:16:11,976
As you wish, Count Dooku.

215
00:16:28,909 --> 00:16:32,496
<i>Sir, a Republic attack fleet
has just entered orbit,</i>

216
00:16:32,580 --> 00:16:33,914
<i>and is approaching the city.</i>

217
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,376
Get me Count Dooku.

218
00:16:37,459 --> 00:16:41,338
<i>It appears Count Dooku has
left the planet's surface.</i>

219
00:16:41,422 --> 00:16:42,423
What?

220
00:16:42,506 --> 00:16:44,842
<i>And the Separatist forces
are in full retreat.</i>

221
00:16:45,676 --> 00:16:47,511
<i>We are alone.</i>

222
00:17:16,707 --> 00:17:19,043
Rex, hold the droid forces here.

223
00:17:19,126 --> 00:17:21,587
-I'm gonna push on and get Padmé.
-Copy that.

224
00:17:34,433 --> 00:17:36,060
Such plans I had.

225
00:17:37,186 --> 00:17:40,606
You know, I've spent
so much of my life misunderstood.

226
00:17:41,649 --> 00:17:43,734
What will they say about me now?

227
00:17:43,817 --> 00:17:45,361
What will I have left behind?

228
00:17:46,111 --> 00:17:48,989
Clovis, you have to turn yourself in.

229
00:17:58,874 --> 00:18:00,501
It's over, Clovis.

230
00:18:11,762 --> 00:18:13,180
Stay away from me.

231
00:18:13,264 --> 00:18:16,016
I didn't do anything wrong.
You have to believe me.

232
00:18:16,475 --> 00:18:18,811
You don't wanna do this.

233
00:18:19,061 --> 00:18:22,106
You don't understand.
You've all been deceived.

234
00:18:22,189 --> 00:18:23,607
Yeah, by you.

235
00:18:23,941 --> 00:18:25,985
No, by Dooku.

236
00:18:27,695 --> 00:18:29,655
I'm not the villain here.
Tell him, Padmé.

237
00:18:31,198 --> 00:18:32,449
Let me go, Clovis.

238
00:19:02,938 --> 00:19:04,148
No!

239
00:19:12,573 --> 00:19:14,950
I can't hold both of you.

240
00:19:17,244 --> 00:19:18,495
Let me go.

241
00:19:18,579 --> 00:19:20,331
No, Anakin, don't!

242
00:19:24,752 --> 00:19:26,086
Try and climb.

243
00:19:28,714 --> 00:19:30,090
I am.

244
00:19:30,382 --> 00:19:31,925
I'm losing you.

245
00:19:32,801 --> 00:19:34,678
I'm sorry, Padmé.

246
00:19:36,555 --> 00:19:37,556
No!

247
00:19:51,779 --> 00:19:54,323
It's okay. You're okay.

248
00:19:54,406 --> 00:19:57,284
I'm sorry, Anakin. I'm sorry.

249
00:19:58,243 --> 00:20:00,954
It's over now. It's all over now.

250
00:20:06,794 --> 00:20:10,881
<i>It is clear to the Banking Clan
it was Rush Clovis</i>

251
00:20:10,964 --> 00:20:14,927
<i>who was behind the corruption
that almost caused our collapse.</i>

252
00:20:15,010 --> 00:20:19,723
<i>In hope of a better tomorrow,
we cede control of the banks</i>

253
00:20:19,807 --> 00:20:23,644
<i>to the office of the Chancellor
of the Galactic Republic.</i>

254
00:20:27,106 --> 00:20:33,946
<i>It is with great humility that
I take on this immense responsibility.</i>

255
00:20:34,655 --> 00:20:37,950
<i>Rest assured,
when the Clone Wars end,</i>

256
00:20:38,033 --> 00:20:41,662
<i>I shall reinstate the banks
as we once knew them.</i>

257
00:20:42,579 --> 00:20:45,707
<i>But during these treacherous times,</i>

258
00:20:46,291 --> 00:20:48,919
<i>we cannot, in good conscience,
allow our money</i>

259
00:20:49,002 --> 00:20:53,924
<i>to fall under the manipulations
of a madman like Count Dooku</i>

260
00:20:54,007 --> 00:20:55,926
<i>or Separatist control again.</i>

261
00:21:00,097 --> 00:21:05,853
<i>May there be prosperity and stability
at all our Republic lands.</i>

262
00:21:06,353 --> 00:21:10,190
<i>May our people be free and safe.</i>

263
00:21:11,024 --> 00:21:12,901
<i>Long live the banks.</i>

264
00:21:13,527 --> 00:21:17,448
<i>Long live the banks!
Long live the banks!</i>

265
00:21:17,531 --> 00:21:18,907
<i>Long live the banks!</i>

266
00:21:18,931 --> 00:21:23,931
http://hiqve.com/

